DESCRIPTION:The Copilot Extensibility Community Call takes place on the 2nd
  Wednesday of each month at 8am PT.\n\nDuring the call\, we demonstrate ti
 ps and tools to help you build powerful solutions that extend Microsoft 36
 5 Copilot (Agent Builder\, Declarative Agents\, Custom Engine Agents\, Fou
 ndry Agents\, etc.)\, Copilot Cowork\, Microsoft Scout\, and Microsoft IQ 
 (including Foundry IQ\, Work IQ\, Fabric IQ\, Web IQ\, and more).\n\nWe al
 so cover the latest news in Microsoft 365 Copilot extensibility. You'll ha
 ve the opportunity to meet members of the Copilot Extensibility product te
 am and community experts\, and to get your questions answered.\n\nYou can 
 learn more about Copilot Extensibility by visiting: https://aka.ms/Copilot
 DevCamp\n\nJoin the call here: https://aka.ms/community/CopilotExtensibility-call-jo
 in\n\nAdditional Resources\nFollow us on:\n- X: https://x.com/Microsoft365
 Dev\n- LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/microsoft365dev\n- Face
 book: https://www.facebook.com/M365Dev\n\nYouTube: https://www.youtube.com
 /channel/UCV_6HOhwxYLXAGd-JOqKPoQ\n\nSubscribe to our Microsoft 365  Devel
 oper YouTube channel  (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCV_6HOhwxYLXAGd-JO
 qKPoQ) for developer  videos and to our Microsoft Community Learning YouTu
 be channel (https://www.youtube.com/@MicrosoftCommunityLearning) to access
  all the community learning content (includes previous call recordings).
